<HEAD>
<TITLE> The International Committee of the Red Cross and  humanitarian  assistance - A policy analysis<BR>
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<P>
<P>
<P>
<TABLE>
<TR valign=top><TD>
<P><IMG SRC="/gifsICRC/IconICRC.gif" ALIGN=left HSPACE=10></TD><TD>
