<TITLE>What's New at the NREL</TITLE>
<H1>What's New at the NREL</H1>
<HR>
<P>
<I>February 13, 1996</I> - The NREL November-December 1995 and January 1996 News Notes is here!  Look under
"Current Activities - The NREL News Notes" on the home page.  This also includes
a list of current seminars at NREL.<BR><I>(tlb)</I><P>
<I>February 13, 1996</I> - Job Announcements at the NREL.  There are several job
announcements under "Open Positions" on the home page.  The position titles are:
<UL>
  <LI> Research Associate (Data Manager), apply before February 29
  <LI> Atmospheric Scientist, apply before March 5
<I>(tlb)</I>
</UL>
<I>November 13, 1995</I> - Job Announcements at the NREL.  There are several job
announcements under "Open Positions" on the home page.  The position titles are:
<UL>
  <LI> Research Associate (Technician), apply before December 15
  <LI> Research Associate (Taxonomy), apply before December 20
  <LI> Research Associate (Lab Manager), apply before January 15
<I>(tlb)</I>
</UL>

<I>November 13, 1995</I> - The NREL August-October News Notes is here!  Look under
"Current Activities - The NREL News Notes" on the home page.  This also includes
a list of current seminars at NREL.<BR><I>(tlb)</I><P>
<I>May 25, 1995</I> - The NREL Brochure is online!  Look under "About the NREL".
Note: some figures still need to be added.<BR><I>(tlb)</I><P> 
<I>May 20, 1995</I> - The NREL People pages.  These pages contain information
such as addresses, phone numbers, job titles and areas of interest.  Coming
soon will be links to CV's and current projects.<BR><I>(tlb)</I><P>
<I>April 3, 1995</I> - The NREL News Notes can be accessed through "Current Activities".
This WWW version of News Notes has a hyper text index
to topics and  a link to previous NREL News Notes.<BR>
<I>(tlb)</I><P>
<I>April 3, 1995</I> - An "NREL Seminars" link was added to the home page.  This links
to the seminar section in the NREL News Notes. <BR>
<I>(tlb)</I><P>

