<TITLE>NREL Scientific Publications</TITLE>
<H1>NREL Scientific Publications</H1>
<HR>
 <IMG SRC="http://www.nrel.colostate.edu/icons/sm_construct.gif"> This page
is under constuction.  Currently key words are pulled from the title.<IMG SRC="http://www.nrel.colostate.edu/icons/sm_construct.gif">

<P>
Publications will be stored in an Oracle database and which can be searched by several
methods.  The search will bring up a list of publication citations.
Currently it searches a nearly complete list of publication citations.
