  <LI><A HREF="BIGHORN.html">Restoration of Bighorn Sheep to National Parks Ecosystems</A>
  <LI><A HREF="ELK.html">Consequences of Human Develpement Activities on Colorado Elk</A>
  <LI><A HREF="U-MGT.html">U-MGT</A> - Population Estimation, Plant Interactions, Forage Biomass and Offtake, and Carrying Capacity Estimation of Elk in the Estes Valley
  <LI><A HREF="FRESH.html">Density estimation of freshwater shrimp using distance sampling</A>
